org.dedda.games.scheisse.exception

Class ExceptionCode

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dedda.games.scheisse.exception.ExceptionCode

  • public abstract class ExceptionCode
extends java.lang.Object
    Class for central collection of all possible exit codes of the program.

    In this class, all possible exit codes ever used by the program except exiting due to RuntimeExceptions are collected. This should prevent unknown or undefined status codes while coding and running the program.

    Created by dedda on 4/24/14.

    Author:
    dedda
